* &quot;The Adventures of Robin Hood&quot; (1955) (Two episodes)) - Will Scarlet two episodes)
* &quot;The Adventures of Aggie&quot; (1956) (Season 1, episode 6: &quot;The Chiseller&quot;) - Heinrich
* &quot;Mary Britten, M.D.&quot; (1958) - Stephen Britten
