*Rhun &quot;Hir&quot; ap Maelgwn (, c. 500)
*Beli ap Rhun
*Iago ap Beli (died c. 616)
*Cadfan ap Iago (c. 565)
*Cadwallon ap Cadfan (d. 634)
*Cadafael ap Cynfeddw ()
*Cadwaladr &quot;Fendigaid&quot; ap Cadwallon (, d. 664)
*Idwal &quot;Iwrch&quot; ap Cadwaladr (Idwal Roebuck, c. 660)
*Rhodri &quot;Molwynog&quot; ap Idwal (, d. 754) 
*Caradog ap Meirion (d. 798, Prince of Rhos)
*Cynan &quot;Dindaethwy&quot; ap Rhodri (d. 816)
*Hywel ap Caradog
*Merfyn &quot;Frych&quot; ap Gwriad (d. 844)

====Princes of Dogfeiling====

*Dogfael ap Cunedda Wledig (c. 410)
*Elno ap Dogfael (c. 440)
*Glas ap Elno (c. 470)
*Elgud ap Glas ap Elno (c. 500)
